  "The most translated film library in the world": "世界上翻译最多的电影资料库",
  "Decades of translation work, carried by trusted ministry partners, have built a library with thousands of language tracks so people can encounter the story of Jesus in the language that reaches them deepest.": "数十年来，在值得信赖的事工伙伴的翻译下，我们建立了一个拥有数千种语言的图书馆，这样人们就可以用对他们影响最深的语言来了解耶稣的故事。",
  "Carrying trusted voices into new formats": "以新的形式传递可信的声音",
  "We are rebuilding how gospel stories are told visually, pairing trusted translations with modern formats so the message can move freely across platforms, cultures, and screen.": "我们正在重建以视觉方式讲述福音故事的方式，将值得信赖的译本与现代格式相结合，使信息能够在不同平台、文化和屏幕上自由传播。",
  "More than a library. A mission-driven team.": "不仅仅是图书馆。一个以使命为导向的团队。",
  "Jesus Film Project is a global team of translators, media specialists, editors, and creators who have served missionaries for decades. We're turning that experience into tools that equip disciple-makers everywhere.": "耶稣电影项目是一个由翻译、媒体专家、编辑和创作者组成的全球性团队，他们为宣教士服务了几十年。我们将这些经验转化为工具，装备各地的门徒造就者。",
  "Next Steps Platform": "下一步工作平台",
  "Connect every viewer with tangible opportunities on their spiritual journey, helping them take a next step into community, Scripture, or mission.": "为每一位观众的灵修之旅提供实实在在的机会，帮助他们向社区、经文或使命迈出下一步。",
  "Evangelistic Media Library": "布道媒体图书馆",
  "We have an extensive Christian media library with thousands of videos, films, and resources available in multiple languages for ministry and evangelism worldwide.": "我们拥有一个内容丰富的基督教媒体图书馆，以多种语言提供数以千计的视频、电影和资源，用于世界各地的事工和传福音工作。",
  "Digital Tools for Ministries": "部委数字工具",
  "Comprehensive digital tools designed specifically for ministry needs, including video management, content distribution, audience engagement, and analytics to help ministries reach more people effectively.": "专为满足事工需求而设计的综合数字工具，包括视频管理、内容发布、受众参与和分析，帮助事工有效地接触更多的人。",
  "Built for global missions": "为全球任务而建",
  "The message doesn't change. The way people watch does.": "信息不会改变。改变的是人们观看的方式。",
  "We are rebuilding our video library and tools from the ground up, committing decades of translation work to the platforms where people already gather, watch, and share.": "我们正在从头开始重建我们的视频库和工具，将数十年的翻译工作投入到人们已经聚集、观看和分享的平台上。",
  "What we are building next": "我们下一步的建设",
